show.description:
An airline tycoon falls for a dazzling air hostess, believing he has found his perfect match.
But when his unsuspecting parents board a flight to meet their future daughter-in-law, a shocking web of arrogance, deceit, and humiliation unravels mid-air.
What began as love soon turns into the costliest mistake of his life.
